                    <span>OS: Windows 11, version 22H2 or newer</span>
                    <span>CPU: AMD Ryzen 2000 Series or newer; Intel Core i3-9100 or newer</span>
                    <span>Security: CPU and motherboard with TPM 2.0 and Secure Boot support</span>
                    <span>RAM: 16 GB</span>
                    <span>Storage: 4 GB available on SATA SSD or better</span>
                    <span>GPU: AMD Radeon RX 550 or NVIDIA GeForce GTX 750 Ti</span>
                    <span>Connection: 10 Mbps or faster wired network</span>
